  <data name="label1.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>For about 10 years
(or days) this game
has been waiting for you, gamer!
For about 10 years
(or days) this adventure
has been waiting for you, pirate!
I don't know who are you,
so let me see you profile,
but before,
answer - Will you a true pirate or no?
Oh, wait, wait, wait!
I am sure, you remember the first part
of LOF - The Ancient Mystery.
Now let me perform
you the second chapter - Magellan's Expediton!</value>
  </data>
  <data name="label2.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>It's easy to guess
that it's about pirates,
bottles (with milk, for sure)
and other silly and ridiculous things!
Will you survive?
Will fight alone
or join real pirate crews?
It's only your choice, my friend!
Don't forget about rum &amp; friends,
pirate ship &amp; some ducks,
your best friends and, for sure,
about maps with treasure chests!
(P.A.R.T.Y. Quests!)
Good luck!
                                                               
                          Christopher Bowes</value>
